EVS Broadcast Equipment Chief L’Hoest Quits Post, Leaves Board

-- B y   J o h n   M a r t e n s
-- 
2011-09-29T16:23:08Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-29/evs-broadcast-equipment-chief-l-hoest-quits-post-leaves-board.html
EVS Broadcasting Equipment SA said
Chief Executive Officer Pierre L’Hoest quit and will also resign
from EVS’s board of directors.  Michel Counson, Jacques Galloy and Luc Doneux will manage
EVS pending a new management structure to be announced next
year.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
John Martens at 
 jmartens1@bloomberg.net  